[Camouflage]: Reduces BRV and HP damage taken by 20%.

Powder Gauge: Holds 2 cartridges.
When Cartridge count is 0 or greater:
 -Prevents KO if HP is at least 50% of Max HP and leaves HP value at 1
When Cartridge count>0:
 -Follows Demon Slaughter with Fated Circle
 -Changes HP Attack, HP Attack+ to Burst Strike
 -If HP drops below 1%, reduces own HP to 1 and triggers Superbollide

Burst Strike: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Gain BRV based on Max BRV (40%).
              1-hit Melee BRV+HP attack.
              Recovers BRV to self based on HP Damage dealt (50%)
Fated Circle: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Gain BRV based on Max BRV (40%).
              1-hit AoE Melee BRV+HP attack.
              Deals split HP damage.
Superbollide: Consumes 1 Cartridge.
              Grants BRV to self based on HP Damage taken in last 2 turns (30%)
              Grants [Superbollide] to self for 2 actions
[Superbollide]: Nullifies all incoming damage to self.

